      "review_summary": "The PR adds route-aware Codex plugin diagnostic suppression, wires it into config validation and doctor stale-plugin scans, preserves PI/OpenClaw session pins during legacy route repair, normalizes OpenAI provider config lookup, and adds regression tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +236, Tests +592, Config -2, Other -53. Total +773 across 13 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current main emits missing/stale plugin diagnostics without considering resolved PI/OpenClaw OpenAI runtime policy, and the PR supplies terminal `openclaw doctor` output for the changed paths. I did not run the doctor command locally because this review was read-only.",
